  {
   "id": "text-1040",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 790,
   "y": 90,
   "width": 1049.4,
   "height": 150.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 32240,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 100880,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "1. Contracts built against mocks ×3:  multiqlti expects {chunks}, the real search returns {hits};  sre-harness calls list_entities —\n    NOT among Omniscience's 13 MCP tools;  the PB-SRE collector pushes topology only to a dry-run mock.\n    → Omniscience needs a VERSIONED MCP contract + conformance tests for consumers.\n2. Doc drift in every repo: Omniscience README says 'pre-v0.1' while v0.2 has shipped; multiqlti PROJECT_STATUS is ~3 months\n    behind; platform-design ADRs 'Accepted' but 'no live AWS resources applied'.\n3. Three 'SRE brains': PB-SRE (advisory, platform-design), autonomous harness (genai-enablement), morning news board (multiqlti).\n    Boundaries fixed only in ADR-0055 — still Proposed, no tracking issue.\n4. No live environment: the platform (EKS/AWS) is designed, not deployed; nowhere to close the e2e loop yet.",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 15,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "1. Contracts built against mocks ×3:  multiqlti expects {chunks}, the real search returns {hits};  sre-harness calls list_entities —\n    NOT among Omniscience's 13 MCP tools;  the PB-SRE collector pushes topology only to a dry-run mock.\n    → Omniscience needs a VERSIONED MCP contract + conformance tests for consumers.\n2. Doc drift in every repo: Omniscience README says 'pre-v0.1' while v0.2 has shipped; multiqlti PROJECT_STATUS is ~3 months\n    behind; platform-design ADRs 'Accepted' but 'no live AWS resources applied'.\n3. Three 'SRE brains': PB-SRE (advisory, platform-design), autonomous harness (genai-enablement), morning news board (multiqlti).\n    Boundaries fixed only in ADR-0055 — still Proposed, no tracking issue.\n4. No live environment: the platform (EKS/AWS) is designed, not deployed; nowhere to close the e2e loop yet.",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
