   "text": "• Pipeline of 7 SDLC stage classes: plan → arch →\n  dev → test → review → deploy → monitor (+fact-check)\n• Strategies: Debate / MoA / Voting / DAG / Swarm\n• Providers: Claude, Gemini, Grok, Ollama, vLLM\n  + CLI subscriptions (claude, agy)\n• RAG: own pgvector → Omniscience (feature flag,\n  local fallback stays)\n• Workspace indexing → becomes an Omniscience\n  connector (memory-architecture ADR, Accepted)\n• Exposes its own MCP: run_pipeline, get_run, …\n• Federation, skills market, guardrails, sandbox\n• ⚠ PROJECT_STATUS ~3 months stale, no CHANGELOG",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 15,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "• Pipeline of 7 SDLC stage classes: plan → arch →\n  dev → test → review → deploy → monitor (+fact-check)\n• Strategies: Debate / MoA / Voting / DAG / Swarm\n• Providers: Claude, Gemini, Grok, Ollama, vLLM\n  + CLI subscriptions (claude, agy)\n• RAG: own pgvector → Omniscience (feature flag,\n  local fallback stays)\n• Workspace indexing → becomes an Omniscience\n  connector (memory-architecture ADR, Accepted)\n• Exposes its own MCP: run_pipeline, get_run, …\n• Federation, skills market, guardrails, sandbox\n• ⚠ PROJECT_STATUS ~3 months stale, no CHANGELOG",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
