  {
   "id": "text-1224",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 110,
   "y": 1382,
   "width": 437.25,
   "height": 225.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 37944,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 118728,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "• Thesis: «intelligence at the edges, determinism\n  at the core»; target L4, never L5\n• Conductor FSM (→Temporal), Gate Engine (Cedar),\n  Verifier: dual-sandbox, model families A ≠ B\n• Curator Console (FastAPI) — real;\n  auto-merge: opt-in, fail-closed, default OFF\n• Knowledge-Plane client to Omniscience — real,\n  static read-only guard (REQ-KP-6)\n• Firecracker / Temporal / OpenBao / SPIRE / Cedar =\n  Python mocks for now («security posture 0%»)\n• ⚠ Phase 1 (load-bearing swaps) not started\n• NOT a multiqlti replacement: peers of different tiers",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 15,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "• Thesis: «intelligence at the edges, determinism\n  at the core»; target L4, never L5\n• Conductor FSM (→Temporal), Gate Engine (Cedar),\n  Verifier: dual-sandbox, model families A ≠ B\n• Curator Console (FastAPI) — real;\n  auto-merge: opt-in, fail-closed, default OFF\n• Knowledge-Plane client to Omniscience — real,\n  static read-only guard (REQ-KP-6)\n• Firecracker / Temporal / OpenBao / SPIRE / Cedar =\n  Python mocks for now («security posture 0%»)\n• ⚠ Phase 1 (load-bearing swaps) not started\n• NOT a multiqlti replacement: peers of different tiers",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
