   "versionNonce": 121056,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "v0.2 shipped (Neo4j+Qdrant cutover) · v0.3/v0.4 in flight · PRs to #311 · most mature component",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "v0.2 shipped (Neo4j+Qdrant cutover) · v0.3/v0.4 in flight · PRs to #311 · most mature component",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
  {
   "id": "text-1256",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1060,
   "y": 818,
   "width": 469.05,
   "height": 375.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 38936,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 121832,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "• Retrieval-only «Insight Mode»: no embedded LLM,\n  answers with citations and provenance; Action Mode = v2\n• ~16 connectors: git, fs, k8s-operator (Go), AWS, S3,\n  Slack, Jira, Datadog, PagerDuty, GitHub PR, alerts, OTel…\n• Pipeline: NATS JetStream → parse (tree-sitter) →\n  chunk → embed (Ollama / OpenAI / Voyage) → index + DLQ\n• Stores: Postgres 16 (metadata) · Qdrant\n  (dense + BM25, RRF) · Neo4j (bitemporal graph, as_of)\n• MCP server: 13 tools — search, get_entity,\n  get_related_entities, blast_radius, replay_context,\n  incident_timeline, resolve_incident, suggest_runbook,\n  find_similar_incidents, generate_postmortem, …\n• REST /api/v1 (~30 routers) + admin UI (React)\n• Workspace tokens fail-closed, scopes, rate limit\n• docker-compose.prod + Helm + operator chart\n• ⚠ README says «pre-v0.1» — contradicts the code\n• ⚠ ingestion→Neo4j/Qdrant not fully wired:\n  fresh installs need migrate_to_hybrid.py\n• ⚠ hardening review 2026-06-10: cross-tenant leak\n  (VETO) and sparse-hash bug caught recently",
   "fontSize": 15,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 15,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "• Retrieval-only «Insight Mode»: no embedded LLM,\n  answers with citations and provenance; Action Mode = v2\n• ~16 connectors: git, fs, k8s-operator (Go), AWS, S3,\n  Slack, Jira, Datadog, PagerDuty, GitHub PR, alerts, OTel…\n• Pipeline: NATS JetStream → parse (tree-sitter) →\n  chunk → embed (Ollama / OpenAI / Voyage) → index + DLQ\n• Stores: Postgres 16 (metadata) · Qdrant\n  (dense + BM25, RRF) · Neo4j (bitemporal graph, as_of)\n• MCP server: 13 tools — search, get_entity,\n  get_related_entities, blast_radius, replay_context,\n  incident_timeline, resolve_incident, suggest_runbook,\n  find_similar_incidents, generate_postmortem, …\n• REST /api/v1 (~30 routers) + admin UI (React)\n• Workspace tokens fail-closed, scopes, rate limit\n• docker-compose.prod + Helm + operator chart\n• ⚠ README says «pre-v0.1» — contradicts the code\n• ⚠ ingestion→Neo4j/Qdrant not fully wired:\n  fresh installs need migrate_to_hybrid.py\n• ⚠ hardening review 2026-06-10: cross-tenant leak\n  (VETO) and sparse-hash bug caught recently",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
