   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
  {
   "id": "text-1288",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 2170,
   "y": 520,
   "width": 408.1,
   "height": 245.0,
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 39928,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 124936,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "boundElements": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "text": "• Vision: «GenAI Value Lab» — Enable, Don't Own;\n  DORA metrics; financial-services compliance (SR 11-7)\n• Pillars: DevOps/SRE workflows, tooling, reliability,\n  codegen, AI architecture + compliance\n• SRE harness: «the harness is the product»\n  (anchor: agents resolve ~11% of incidents — ITBench)\n• Autonomy tiers T1→T4 + action-tier table;\n  degrade one tier down on low confidence\n• Change gate: PROCEED / BLOCK / REQUIRE_HUMAN —\n  deterministic, no LLM; rollback has no LLM either\n• PlatformGraph port + OmniscienceMcpPlatformGraph\n• CI gates: GitLab CI, ArgoCD PreSync, Argo Rollouts\n• All harness stages merged to main (July 2026):\n  eval, gate CLI, multi-check, agentops, Sentinel ADR",
   "fontSize": 14,
   "fontFamily": 6,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "baseline": 14,
   "containerId": null,
   "originalText": "• Vision: «GenAI Value Lab» — Enable, Don't Own;\n  DORA metrics; financial-services compliance (SR 11-7)\n• Pillars: DevOps/SRE workflows, tooling, reliability,\n  codegen, AI architecture + compliance\n• SRE harness: «the harness is the product»\n  (anchor: agents resolve ~11% of incidents — ITBench)\n• Autonomy tiers T1→T4 + action-tier table;\n  degrade one tier down on low confidence\n• Change gate: PROCEED / BLOCK / REQUIRE_HUMAN —\n  deterministic, no LLM; rollback has no LLM either\n• PlatformGraph port + OmniscienceMcpPlatformGraph\n• CI gates: GitLab CI, ArgoCD PreSync, Argo Rollouts\n• All harness stages merged to main (July 2026):\n  eval, gate CLI, multi-check, agentops, Sentinel ADR",
   "lineHeight": 1.25
  },
